      <abstract>
        <p>The fate of the Jews of Biecz under German occupation. Executions, liquidation of the
          ghetto in August 1942. In February 1942, the author survived an execution in which his
          family perished and he found shelter with Adela Jędrzejowska in Moszczenica.</p>
      </abstract>
